name: User should not be able to search items after entering invalid data
User should be able to add most expensive searched item to the cart
User should be able to see tees products image, price, reviews and "Add To Cart" button appears on mouse over
User should not be able to submit a form with non-existing order id and the rest valid data
User should see banners & content on the main page
User should be able to reset password and log in using new one
User should be able to add product from wishlist to cart

User should be able to sort items by product name and price in descending and ascending directions
User should be able to create an account and then log out
